# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s4_talk.rpy:17
translate english ch1_s4_talk_14b66ca0:

    # "萧炎哥哥。"
    "Brother Xiao Yan."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s4_talk.rpy:19
translate english ch1_s4_talk_c2e61744:

    # "在经过少年身旁时，少女顿下了脚步，对着萧炎恭敬的弯了弯腰，美丽的俏脸上，居然露出了让周围少女为之嫉妒的清雅笑容。"
    "When passing by the boy, the girl paused, bowed respectfully to Xiao Yan, and on her beautiful face, actually revealed an elegant smile that made the surrounding girls jealous."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s4_talk.rpy:21
translate english ch1_s4_talk_69a8cd9c:

    # xy "我现在还有资格让你怎么叫么？"
    xy "Do I still deserve to be called that by you?"

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s4_talk.rpy:23
translate english ch1_s4_talk_adca33a7:

    # "望着面前这颗已经成长为家族中最璀璨的明珠，萧炎苦涩的道，她是在自己落魄后，极为少数还对自己依旧保持着尊敬的人。"
    "Looking at the brightest pearl of the clan that had grown up before him, Xiao Yan spoke bitterly. She was one of the very few who still maintained respect for him after his fall."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s4_talk.rpy:25
translate english ch1_s4_talk_65c7cc92:

    # xx "萧炎哥哥，以前你曾经与薰儿说过，要能放下，才能拿起，提放自如，是自在人！"
    xx "Brother Xiao Yan, you once told Xun'er that one must be able to let go to be able to pick up. To handle things with ease is to be a free person!"

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s4_talk.rpy:27
translate english ch1_s4_talk_5c08d3c7:

    # "萧薰儿微笑着柔声道，略微稚嫩的嗓音，却是暖人心肺。"
    "Xiao Xun'er said softly with a smile, her slightly immature voice warming the heart."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s4_talk.rpy:32
translate english ch1_s4_talk_3dcac28f:

    # xy "呵呵，自在人？我也只会说而已，你看我现在的模样，象自在人吗？而且……这世界，本来就不属于我。"
    xy "Hehe, a free person? I can only say it. Look at me now, do I look like a free person? Besides... this world didn't belong to me anyway."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s4_talk.rpy:34
translate english ch1_s4_talk_bd4c0afb:

    # "萧炎自嘲的一笑，意兴阑珊的道。"
    "Xiao Yan smiled self-mockingly and said with a lack of interest."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s4_talk.rpy:39
translate english ch1_s4_talk_07092cb3:

    # "面对着萧炎的颓废，萧薰儿纤细的眉毛微微皱了皱，认真的道："
    "Facing Xiao Yan's decadence, Xiao Xun'er's slender eyebrows frowned slightly, and she said seriously:"

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s4_talk.rpy:41
translate english ch1_s4_talk_4413e614:

    # xx "萧炎哥哥，虽然并不知道你究竟是怎么回事，不过，薰儿相信，你会重新站起来，取回属于你的荣耀与尊严……"
    xx "Brother Xiao Yan, although I don't know exactly what happened to you, Xun'er believes that you will stand up again and reclaim the glory and dignity that belong to you..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s4_talk.rpy:46
translate english ch1_s4_talk_980d7309:

    # "话到此处，微顿了顿，少女白皙的俏脸，头一次露出淡淡的绯红："
    "At this point, she paused slightly, and a faint blush appeared on the girl's fair face for the first time:"

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s4_talk.rpy:48
translate english ch1_s4_talk_5f5e451e:

    # xx "当年的萧炎哥哥，的确很吸引人……"
    xx "The Brother Xiao Yan from back then was indeed very attractive..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s4_talk.rpy:53
translate english ch1_s4_talk_6fbbba59:

    # xy "呵呵……"
    xy "Hehe..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s4_talk.rpy:55
translate english ch1_s4_talk_615e8740:

    # "面对着少女毫不掩饰的坦率话语，少年尴尬的笑了一声，可却未再说什么，人不风流枉少年，可现在的他，实在没这资格与心情，落寞的回转过身，对着广场之外缓缓行去……"
    "Facing the girl's undisguised frank words, the boy laughed awkwardly but said nothing more. A youth without romance is a youth wasted, but now, he really didn't have the qualification or mood. He turned around lonely and slowly walked out of the square..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s4_talk.rpy:60
translate english ch1_s4_talk_241b4548:

    # "站在原地望着少年那恍如与世隔绝的孤独背影，萧薰儿踌躇了一会，然后在身后一干嫉妒的狼嚎声中，快步追了上去，与少年并肩而行……"
    "Standing in place, looking at the boy's lonely back that seemed cut off from the world, Xiao Xun'er hesitated for a moment, then amidst the jealous howls behind her, quickly chased after him and walked side by side with the boy..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s4_talk.rpy:66
translate english ch1_s4_talk_aa504e23:

    # "第一章 完"
    "Chapter 1 End"
